OL,3,CIngram-Moores 'made more than #1m from
OL,4,Cfamily link to Captain Tom Foundation'
OL,6,FThe family of renowned pandemic
OL,7,Ffundraiser Captain Sir Tom Moore made
OL,8,Fmore than a million pounds through
OL,9,Ftheir association with the charity set
OL,10,Fup in his name, a damning report has
OL,11,Ffound.
OL,13,FThe charities watchdog concluded there
OL,14,Fhad been repeated instances of
OL,15,Fmisconduct by the veteran's daughter,
OL,16,FHannah Ingram-Moore and her husband,
OL,17,FColin.
