OL,6,FSir Tom became a household name in the
OL,7,Fpandemic, raising millions for NHS
OL,8,Fcharities by walking laps of his
OL,9,Fgarden in lockdown.
OL,11,FBut separately, a #1.4 million book
OL,12,Fdeal and an #18,000 awards ceremony
OL,13,Fappearance fee were among the
OL,14,Ffinancial benefits Mr and Mrs Ingram-
OL,15,FMoore enjoyed through their family
OL,16,Flinks to the Captain Tom Foundation.
OL,18,FA spokesperson for the foundation said
OL,19,Fit is "imploring the Ingram-Moores to
OL,20,Frectify matters by returning the funds
OL,21,Fdue" to the charity.
