OL,6,FThe commission has called on the
OL,7,FIngram-Moores to make a "suitable
OL,8,Fdonation" ` declining to say how much
OL,9,F` from the book advance deal, to
OL,10,F"honour the commitment that Captain
OL,11,FTom, in his own words in his first
OL,12,Fbook, stated in the foreword about the
OL,13,Fmoney benefiting the foundation set up
