OL,7,Fthey are "pleased with the Charity
OL,8,FCommission's unequivocal findings
OL,9,Fregarding the Ingram-Moores'
OL,10,Fmisconduct".
OL,12,FThey added: "We join the Charity
OL,13,FCommission in imploring the Ingram-
OL,14,FMoores to rectify matters by returning
OL,15,Fthe funds due to the Foundation, so
OL,16,Fthat they can be donated to well-
OL,17,Fdeserving charities as intended by the
OL,18,Flate Captain Sir Tom Moore.
OL,20,F"We hope they do so immediately and
