OL,6,F` "Disingenuous" statements from Mrs
OL,7,FIngram-Moore about not being offered a
OL,8,Fsix-figure sum to become the charity's
OL,9,Fchief executive, when she had in fact
OL,10,Fset out expectations for a #150,000
OL,11,Fremuneration package before taking on
OL,12,Fthe role.
