OL,6,F` Confusion over handling of
OL,7,Fintellectual property rights, which
OL,8,Fthe commission said were owned by the
OL,9,Ffamily but offered to the foundation
OL,10,Fto use without appropriate agreements
OL,11,Fin place, leading to possible
OL,12,Ffinancial losses to the charity.
