OL,6,FIn July, the Ingram-Moores released a
OL,7,Fstatement saying they had been banned
OL,8,Ffrom being charity trustees,
OL,9,Fdescribing the commission's
OL,10,Finvestigation as a "harrowing and
OL,11,Fdebilitating ordeal" and a "relentless
OL,12,Fpursuit".
OL,14,FIn an interview with the PA news
OL,15,Fagency, David Holdsworth, commission
OL,16,Fchief executive, insisted the inquiry
OL,17,Fhas been fair and balanced, saying:
OL,18,F"We are relentless as a regulator and,
OL,19,Fyes, we will follow wrongdoing where
OL,20,Fwhere we find it in the sector."
