OL,7,Fboth ` meaning Mrs Ingram-Moore cannot
OL,8,Fbe a trustee or hold a senior
OL,9,Fmanagement role in any charity in
OL,10,FEngland and Wales for 10 years, nor Mr
OL,11,FIngram-Moore for eight years ` were
