OL,6,FHe told PA: "As the report sets out,
OL,7,Fthere was a book deal agreed for #1.4
OL,8,Fmillion which the Ingram-Moores
OL,9,Fbenefited from. There was the payment
OL,10,Fof a fee for an award ceremony for
OL,11,F#18,000 which Mrs Ingram Moore
OL,12,Freceived directly, not the charity.
OL,14,F"And so I think if you read the
OL,15,Freport, the public can draw their own
OL,16,Fconclusions about the total amount of
OL,17,Fprivate benefit the Ingram-Moores have
OL,18,Fachieved through their association
OL,19,Fwith the charity."
