OL,6,FMr Holdsworth said the foundation had
OL,7,F"not lived up to that legacy of others
OL,8,Fbefore self, which is central to
OL,9,Fcharity".
OL,11,FHe added: "The public, and the law,
OL,12,Frightly expect those involved in
OL,13,Fcharities to make an unambiguous
OL,14,Fdistinction between their personal
OL,15,Finterests and those of the charity and
OL,16,Fthe beneficiaries they are there to
OL,17,Fserve.
